window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Breaking the coach's rule not to date his daughter? When she's my fated mate, I have to play a forbidden game of love.</b></p> <p>Madison: Transferring to Bay State University is my escape from the bullies at my old school, who think just because I'm plus-size, I shouldn't play sports. Since my dad is the coach of the football team, I can move in with him and make my plans for my own training center for women like me. I don't have time for much more than school and workâ€¦ and crushing on the biggest defensive player on the Dire Wolves team.</p> <p>Luka: I'm the defense football star the guys want to be, and the girls want to be with. Only a few know that I'm also a wolf shifter, including Coach. The day he introduces us to his daughter, I know she's my fated mate. But he's declared her off limits, forbidden. There's no denying the pull, and when danger threatens her, I have to reveal my true nature to keep her safe.</p> <p>I'll fight for what fate has given me, even if it gets me kicked off the team. But with my place on the team and in the university at risk, Madison's fear of confrontation could threaten everything before we've even truly begun.</p> <p><b><i>Big D Wolf</i></b><b> is a fated mates wolf shifter and plus size heroine romance with secrets, passion, and a love that breaks all rules. Luka and Madison's story is the newest installment in the Big Wolf on Campus series, and their story proves that true love can conquer anything. Even a coach's whistle.</b></p>"; 
